Job Details
Sales manager required as a permanent contract based at our Head Office in Jebil Ali. Overseeing and managing the full sales department within the UAE, KSA and surrounding GCC countries.
To manage and organise a sales team of 8-10 persons and reporting back to the GM and CEO and to implement strategies provided by managment on further expansion into new markets within the surrounding countries. Responsible for the day to day running of our sales team, conducting monthly sales meetings and reporting back with weekly reports to the management.
Requirements
Previous Experience – 3 years in Sales Management
